title: Organico
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, International, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic cafe and juice bar inside a health food store. Mostly vegan food and includes raw items like spaghetti and meatballs, desserts and snacks. Has tuna salad (vegan substitute available) and may use other non-vegan ingredients on occasion. Sample entrees such as Indian rice; bok choy with organic onion; forbidden black rice; happy bowls.
